<h1 id="basic-idea-core--edges-between-vertices-and-faces-verticesfaces-consist-only-of-an-id-and-a-reference-to-an-outgoingcircling-edge">basic idea: core = edges between vertices and faces, vertices/faces consist only of an id and a reference to an outgoing/circling edge</h1>
<h1 id="edges-are-directed-origin-and-destination-vertexface">edges are directed (origin and destination vertex/face)</h1>
<h1 id="edges-come-in-a-package-of-for-edges-each-that-form-a-quad-edge-their-opposite-origin-and-destination-swapped-rotated-90-left-and-roated-90-right">edges come in a ‚Äúpackage‚Äù of for edges each, that form a quad-edge; their opposite (origin and destination swapped), rotated 90¬∞ left and roated 90¬∞ right</h1>
<h1 id="each-edge-knows-its-origin-the-other-edges-in-its-quad-edge-and-the-next-edge-around-its-origin-in-counter-clockwise-order">each edge knows: its origin, the other edges in its quad-edge and the next edge around its origin in counter-clockwise order</h1>

<h1 id="navigation-is-based-on-the-symrotinv_rot-and-the-next-edge-of-an-edge">navigation is based on the sym/rot/inv_rot and the next-edge of an edge</h1>
